{"tid":34721,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[正能量] 大家對上次笑係幾時？","createTime":"2016-12-11T15:51:08.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T16:12:44.000Z","uid":61965,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"19c0b44163f30ecbd3efed9ed058243447aa44f5","tid":34721,"uid":61965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:51:08.000Z","msg":"唔知各位巴打對上次因為一件事物嘅發生覺得開心快樂而笑係幾時？因為期待第二天嘅來臨而笑住訓係幾時？<br />\n無論你幾唔開心,同屋企人關系唔好,冇朋友定做任何野唔如意嘅你<br />\n不如諗下啲開心野舒緩下情緒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如...回憶番舊時追女仔嘅畫面。<br />\n日子總會來臨,不如正面咁面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：係whatsapp群一留言冇人覆我理我而同又寄人籬下睇人面色嘅毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ec8b6d2e0a4e9861e5bdc5d378e4cfdd99b90d","tid":34721,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:52:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇膠post sor 個人係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"963d1211ddeeb3455e99f202d4bc23ace6590c56","tid":34721,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:53:55.000Z","msg":"上年"},{"pid":"b09e53d3b2b882c16c8cb9f9ee79d6f3217c2b3d","tid":34721,"uid":63648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T16:12:44.000Z","msg":"嗰陣同佢一齊 大家放緊假<br />\n朝早搭個半鐘巴士去佢屋企<br />\n拎早餐上去一齊食 食完一齊訓 訓到晏晝<br />\n訓醒落街買餸 一齊煮飯 <br />\n食飽就玩下貓 望下窗外面既後山<br />\n然後hea下訓下 一齊睇下動漫<br />\n六七點左右就落街食飯<br />\n食完去海傍行下坐下<br />\n行到攰攰地 送佢返屋企<br />\n然後自己再搭夜車番去<br />\n<br />\n食飽就訓 訓醒就食<br />\n豬一般既生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢啲日子<br />\n已經花光今年的運氣<img src=\"/a